00:23:27.520 --> 00:23:32.000
This helps you get consistent branding without a lot of effort, ensuring your work consistently

00:23:32.000 --> 00:23:37.040
follows brand guidelines and avoids duplication by defining branding in one file.

00:23:39.839 --> 00:23:44.319
Brand.yaml also makes it really easy to collaborate. You can share a single brand.yaml

00:23:44.560 --> 00:23:48.640
file across your organization to ensure everyone can easily apply the same branding.

00:23:50.479 --> 00:23:55.199
Another thing is that we've been talking about using brand.yaml for use in your organization,

00:23:55.199 --> 00:24:00.079
but there are other things you might want branding for. You might want to develop a personal brand.yaml

00:24:00.079 --> 00:24:04.319
and use it across your websites and talk to create a consistent personal brand.

00:24:05.119 --> 00:24:11.520
I use brand.yaml for these slides, so if I want to use this theme in the future, I can just use

00:24:11.680 --> 00:24:15.680
this theme in the future. I can just use that same yaml file.

00:24:18.319 --> 00:24:20.479
Great, so thanks for coming to this presentation,

00:24:20.479 --> 00:24:26.239
and I am looking forward to your questions in the Q&A.

